he method is\nillustrated by numerical experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2012 03:47:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2013 07:46:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-17"}
