totic time limit. The\nnon-averaged heterogeneous SFD systems display a lack of self-averaging. An\nexponential with a power-law argument, multiplied by a power-law pre-factor is\nshown to describe well the FPTD for all times for homogeneous SFD and\nsub-diffusive fBm systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2012 10:14:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-10"}
