 growth of metallic\ninverse opals prepared by electrochemical crystallization of matter, so the\ntheoretical results can be compared with experimental data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 May 2012 14:21:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-10"}
